SENATE AMENDMENT

SENATE AMENDMENT “ ” to COMMITTEE AMENDMENT “A” to H.P. 145, L.D. 222
1 SUMMARY
22 This amendment amends Committee Amendment "A" by replacing the appropriations
33 and allocations section with a baseline allocation of $500. It clarifies that the Department
44 of Environmental Protection may receive funds, grants or contributions from public or
55 private sources to design and implement the program and must design and implement the
66 program only when funds are available.
